//           "1. Well Rested \n\nYou need to know that enough rest is very important for the health of the body. Because if the body is preoccupied with many activities every day and lacks rest, the body will be susceptible to disease. With enough rest every day, you have done how to maintain a healthy lifestyle properly.\n\n\n 2. Aware of Food \n\nFor how to maintain a healthy lifestyle, you need to regulate what foods will be consumed every day. Examples of various kinds of nutrients needed by humans are carbohydrates, proteins, vitamins and minerals. In addition, you should also avoid high-fat foods. those foods can cause the accumulation of cholesterol in blood vessels. This can lead to various chronic diseases.\n\n\n3. Exercise \n\nTaking time to exercise is one way to live a healthy lifestyle. Because exercise makes the body more fit. Exercising can remove toxins in the body, which are released through sweat. Maintaining a healthy lifestyle is incomplete if you don't exercise.",
